# r3blog

blog.mpa.fi created with Rails 3 and hosted in Heroku.

## Features

* Editor for posts (place to paste XHTML formatted post from TextMate)
* Drafts (published_at)
* Comments powered by [Disqus](http://disqus.com/)
* Atom feed
* Heroku RULES, depends heavily on Heroku deployment
* Tags (keywords)
* Page caching with [caches_page_via_http](http://github.com/pedro/caches_page_via_http)

## Missing features

A lot, as always.